        {
            "title": "SHEIN在中美互降關稅後下調在美零售價",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">《彭博》報道，快時尚平台SHEIN在中美互降關稅實施後，下調在美零售價格。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：SHEIN官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250210_FI_source-web_SHEIN-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：SHEIN官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250210_FI_source-web_SHEIN-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：SHEIN官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">報道對SHEIN網站上其中98項商品的價格變化作出統計，顯示這些商品昨天(5月14日)平均售價5.56美元，較上周三(5月7日)高位6.38美元，減價約13%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">受到之前關稅問題影響，SHEIN於上月25日在美零售價開始上調，其後公司在當地銷售一直下跌。報道指出，按信用卡及借記卡交易數據，截至上周日(5月4日)當周銷售額按年跌15%。今次SHEIN在中美互降關稅後迅速下調價格，應是希望令銷售情況盡快改善。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">報道引述SHEIN向美國消費者發送價格下調通知，宣傳多種款式的價格降低，並承諾消費者無需支付任何因關稅引起的費用或額外成本。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14931433-shein%e5%9c%a8%e4%b8%ad%e7%be%8e%e4%ba%92%e9%99%8d%e9%97%9c%e7%a8%85%e5%be%8c%e4%b8%8b%e8%aa%bf%e5%9c%a8%e7%be%8e%e9%9b%b6%e5%94%ae%e5%83%b9",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250210_FI_source-web_SHEIN-4.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-15 16:26:15",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "午後再回 滬指收跌23點 深指挫1.62% 寧德時代中止7連升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地A股午後延續回吐走勢，滬深兩市股指雙雙跌破早市低位，寧德時代(03750)在港IPO中午截止認購，A股亦中止7連升。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_CATL-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_CATL-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指全日報跌，今早初段造出的全日高位3402點亦微跌1點，開市僅約20分鐘跌幅便擴大至逾10點，其後便展開反覆向下之旅，午市中段最多跌25點，低見3378點；滬指收報3380點，仍跌23點或0.68%，成交4612.92億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指今日同樣一直「潛水」，今早低開29點、報10324點即成全日高位，其後便呈一浪低於一浪走勢，並以全日低位收市；深指收報10186點，挫167點或1.62%，成交6911.02億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數也跌36點或0.91%，以3907點收市；創業板指數跌39點或1.92%，報2043點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20190507_FI_A股_FB-1-2-3-1-5_source-ap_-2-1-1-3.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20190507_FI_A股_FB-1-2-3-1-5_source-ap_-2-1-1-3.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">寧德時代A股(300750.SZ)經過之前連升7個交易日累計漲13.43%後，今日終於報跌收市，報260.18元，跌0.92%，成交36.86億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">昨天表現搶眼的保險股今日亦普遍回吐，新華保險(01336)A股(601336.SH)跌幅擴大至2.94%，報51.85元；中國平安(02318)A股(601318.SH)也踳%，報54.25元；中國太保(02601)A股(601601.SH)跌1.99%，報34.04元；中國人壽(02628)A股(601628.SH)跌1.63%，報39.32元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：新華保險官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230725_FI_source-web_01336.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：新華保險官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230725_FI_source-web_01336.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：新華保險官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">生物製藥板塊則重現資金淨流入，藥明康德A股(603259.SH)逆市升0.59%，報61.39元；凱萊英(06821)A股(002821.SZ)升2.91%，報83.05元；諾誠健華(09969)A股(688428.SH)升3.57%，報20.62元；新華製藥(00719)A股(000756.SZ)也跟升1.64%，報14.23元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14931157-%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e5%86%8d%e5%9b%9e-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c23%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%87%e6%8c%ab1-62-%e5%af%a7%e5%be%b7%e6%99%82%e4%bb%a3%e4%b8%ad%e6%ad%a27%e9%80%a3%e5%8d%87",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250407_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097181957222-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-15 15:15:41",
